ivardefs.name: action
ivardefs.desc: The type of processing action being requested, for example Reversal, Readjudication, StatusRequest,PendedRequest.

ivardefs.name: created
ivardefs.desc: The date when this resource was created.

ivardefs.name: exclude_
ivardefs.desc: Names of resource types to exclude.

ivardefs.name: include_
ivardefs.desc: Names of resource types to include.

ivardefs.name: item_
ivardefs.desc: List of top level items to be re-adjudicated, if none specified then the entire submission is re-adjudicated.

ivardefs.name: nullify
ivardefs.desc: If true remove all history excluding audit.

ivardefs.name: organization
ivardefs.desc: The organization which is responsible for the action speccified in this request.

ivardefs.name: period
ivardefs.desc: A period of time during which the fulfilling resources would have been created.

ivardefs.name: provider
ivardefs.desc: The practitioner who is responsible for the action specified in this request.

ivardefs.name: reference
ivardefs.desc: A reference to supply which authenticates the process.

ivardefs.name: request
ivardefs.desc: Reference of resource which is the target or subject of this action.

ivardefs.name: response
ivardefs.desc: Reference of a prior response to resource which is the target or subject of this action.

ivardefs.name: status
ivardefs.desc: The status of the resource instance.

ivardefs.name: target
ivardefs.desc: The organization which is the target of the request.
